        {
            "title": "半日收市︱先漲後回 恒指跌126點報24624點 兩萬五受阻 金融股撐市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地上月官方PMI勝預期，對港股只有短暫刺激，大市今早先揚後倒跌，金融股擔起撐市大旗，中銀香港(02388)績後曾漲逾半成。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中銀香港官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/bplib_20230718-142907_source-web_02388.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中銀香港官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/bplib_20230718-142907_source-web_02388.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中銀香港官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開67點後，初段曾在內地上月官方PMI勝預期、疊加亞洲主要股市跌幅收窄的情況下，一度有上試兩萬五之勢，最高曾見24988點，升237點，可惜其後便重現由高位拾級回吐的走勢，中段開始倒跌，最低曾見24615點，跌135%，尾市僅能在低位徘徊。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中銀香港官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/bplib_20230718-142907_source-web_02388.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中銀香港官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/bplib_20230718-142907_source-web_02388.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中銀香港官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"千問 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251124_FI_source-web_09988-1-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"千問 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251124_FI_source-web_09988-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">千問 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中行官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135518_source-web_中國銀行中行03988-5-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中行官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135518_source-web_中國銀行中行03988-5-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中行官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美的集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240529_FI_source-web_Midea-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美的集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240529_FI_source-web_Midea-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：美的集團官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中銀香港官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/bplib_20230718-142907_source-web_02388.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中銀香港官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"千問 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251124_FI_source-web_09988-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">千問 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中行官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135518_source-web_中國銀行中行03988-5-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中行官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美的集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240529_FI_source-web_Midea-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：美的集團官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指中午收報24624點，跌126點或0.51%。恒生科技指數繼續跑輸大市，半日跌44點或0.94%，報4646點；國企指數跌70點或0.84%，報8328點。主板半日成交1328.5億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4月份期指半日跌118點，報24626點，高水1點。科指期貨跌48點，報4643點，低水3點。國指期貨跌60點，報8329點，高水不足1點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅科股是拖低大市的主力，「ATMXJ」全線報跌。阿里巴巴(09988)的千問正式發布最新一代全模態大模型Qwen3.5-Omni，該股依然高開低走，半日跌1.91%，報118.2元；小米(01810)更挫2.16%，報31.68元；美團(03690)反覆跌0.71%，報83.6元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">「ATMXJ」餘下兩成員齊於尾市轉跌，騰訊(00700)微跌0.08%，報481.2元；京東(09618)開市前公告擬發人民幣計價的優先票據，股價高開低收，報112.8元，蹤8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價今早沖高後略回，「三桶油」借勢回吐，中國石油(00857)挫4.4%，報10.65元；中國海油(00883)也跌3.74%，報27.82元；中國石化(00386)跌0.67%，報4.48元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"千問 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251124_FI_source-web_09988-1-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"千問 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251124_FI_source-web_09988-1-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">千問 (圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其他資源股亦多半偏軟，中國神華(01088)去年盈利倒退，績後該股今早先升後挫，中午收報45.7元，跌4.35%。煤炭股普遍跟跌，中煤能源(01898)跌7.19%，報12.9元；兗礦能源(01171)挫6.06%，報14.41元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，內地金融股則普遍在績後受捧。昨天收市後派成績表的中國銀行(03988)，今早逆市升0.82%，報4.93元，創下逾7年新高；同系中銀香港(02388)績後於今早最高衝上42.84元，漲5.67%，收報42.18元，仍升4.05%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中行官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135518_source-web_中國銀行中行03988-5-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中行官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-135518_source-web_中國銀行中行03988-5-官網影片截圖_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中行官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上周五收市後已公布業績的工商銀行(01398)，今早亦再創逾7年新高，中午收報6.77元，升0.45%；建設銀行(00939)也升0.61%，報8.29元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">績後受捧的藍籌尚有美的集團(00300)與舜宇光學(02382)，兩股均躋身藍籌升幅10大榜上。美的集團漲6.18%，報83.3元，是表現次佳藍籌；舜宇則升1.89%，報54元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美的集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240529_FI_source-web_Midea-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美的集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240529_FI_source-web_Midea-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美的集團官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">位列藍籌升幅榜首的則是翰森製藥(03692)，今早漲6.71%，報35.3元。藥明系同樣明顯跑贏大市，藥明生物(02269)升3.95%，報32.6元；藥明康德(02359)升2.63%，報117.1元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今日再有兩隻新股登場，股價表現迥異。傅里葉(03625)中午收報80.65元，較招股價40元高1.02倍；銅師傅(00664)則報37.3元，較招股價60元低37.83%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15817098-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%85%88%e6%bc%b2%e5%be%8c%e5%9b%9e-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c126%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124624%e9%bb%9e-%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%94%e5%8f%97%e9%98%bb-%e9%87%91",
